<p>1 Document 297.</p>

<p>2 See Document 280.</p>

<p>3 Presumably the Australian-Chinese draft resolution concerning observation of the cease-fire rather than the new Australian draft resolution concerning arbitration (see Document 297, paragraphs 1 and 2 respectively).</p>

<p>4 Document 195.</p>

